name: Delhi Municipal Corporation (Validation of Electricity Tax) Act and Other Laws (Repeal) Act, 2002
1: 1. Short title.This Act may be called the Delhi Municipal Corporation (Validation of Electricity  Tax) Act and Other Laws (Repeal) Act, 2002.
2: 2. Repeal of certain enactments.The enactments specified in the Schedule are hereby repealed to  the extent mentioned in the fourth column thereof.
